### Convert Job - Create a new conversion job
# Response: ConvertJobResponse { jobId, geoRecordId, status }
POST http://localhost:8080/api/job/convert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "geo": {
    "type": "FeatureCollection",
    "features": [
      {
        "type": "Feature",
        "geometry": {
          "type": "Point",
          "coordinates": [-122.4194, 37.7749]
        },
        "properties": {
          "name": "San Francisco"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}

