### Get All Jobs - No filter
# Response: JobListResponse { jobs: [JobSummary], page, pageSize, count }
GET http://localhost:8080/api/job

### Get All Jobs - Filter by PENDING status
# Response: JobListResponse { jobs: [JobSummary], page, pageSize, count }
GET http://localhost:8080/api/job?status=PENDING

### Get All Jobs - Filter by DONE status
# Response: JobListResponse { jobs: [JobSummary], page, pageSize, count }
GET http://localhost:8080/api/job?status=DONE

### Get All Jobs - Filter by PROCESSING status
